# Check-boxes
#+LATEX_HEADER: \setbox0=\hbox{\large$\square$}
#+BIND: org-export-latex-list-parameters (:cbon "[{\\parbox[][][c]{\\wd0}{\\large$\\boxtimes$}}]" :cboff "[{\\parbox[][][c]{\\wd0}{\\large$\\square$}}]")
# Nicer Fonts
#+LATEX_HEADER: \\usepackage{xunicode}
